title: Chest didnt appear in my loot!

embed.description: Imgur: The most awesome images on the Internet.

body:
I earned S rank in my varus game and i havent got any chest! It still shows i havent unlocked it for that champion(see picture)
Pls help!

replies.body: You most likely had already gotten a mastery chest for getting an S with Varus this season. Keep in mind, you can only get one chest per champ per season.
